com.att.aro.pcap.packetRebuild

Class PCapFileWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.pcap.packetRebuild.PCapFileWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CaptureFileWriter

    public class PCapFileWriter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CaptureFileWriter
    Class for creating capture files in libcap format.
    if using java version less then 1.5 then the packet time resolution will be in msec and no nanosec.
    Since:
    java 1.5
    Author:
    roni bar yanai
